OL,5, A stalker who harassed women online by 
OL,6, creating fake social media accounts to 
OL,7, spread lies about them has been jailed.
OL,9,FMatthew Hardy, 30, would relentlessly  
OL,10,Fmessage his victims, leaving them in   
OL,11,Fconstant fear that they were being     
OL,12,Fwatched and what would happen next.    
OL,14,FHe pleaded guilty to stalking involving
OL,15,Ffear of violence and harassment after  
OL,16,Fbreaching a restraining order.         
OL,18,FHardy, from Northwich, Cheshire, was   
OL,19,Fjailed for nine years at Chester Crown 
OL,20,FCourt.                                 
